## 🌐 How to Share With Friends

### ✅ Option 1: GitHub Pages (FREE — Best Option)
Since the app connects directly to Supabase, you can host it anywhere for free!
1. Go to your repo on GitHub → **Settings** → **Pages**
2. Source: **Deploy from a branch**
3. Branch: `main` → `/ (root)`
4. Click **Save**
5. Share the generated link!

### ✅ Option 2: Netlify (FREE — Easiest)
1. Go to [netlify.com](https://netlify.com) and sign up
2. Drag and drop your `skill builder` folder onto the Netlify dashboard
3. You get a link like `https://cool-name-123.netlify.app`
4. Share that link — done!

